  "2190220": {
    "name": "东方弹幕神乐 失落幻想",
    "steam_appid": 2190220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ーーー这个世界，是因灵梦毁灭的啊</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方弹幕神乐 失落幻想》是东方Project官方认证的二次创作音乐动作游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中存在两种模式，分别是通过弹幕神乐（音乐游戏）来解明幻想乡毁灭之谜的“剧情模式”，以及可以尽情畅玩音乐游戏的“自由模式”。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含游戏本体收录的68首乐曲，以及<strong>已公布或已发售</strong>的追加乐曲包第1弹～第14弹全部曲目，总计可体验250首以上乐曲。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方Ｂ站：Alliance Arts </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方微博：盟艺游戏 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方抖音：Alliance Arts </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神乐关卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・随着节奏敲击音符的音乐游戏 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・踩在节奏上连续击中4或6个轨道的全部音符，即可达成连击，获得更多分数 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/0cfe5f30a029e9992c08e28ca3ca2e4e.poster.avif?t=1770887459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/0cfe5f30a029e9992c08e28ca3ca2e4e.webm?t=1770887459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>弹幕关卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・将弹幕射击和音乐游戏结合的全新游戏体验 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・达成各个关卡的条件（任务）即可通关 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/0416877091b182cd224e7fe90321374e.poster.avif?t=1770887459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/0416877091b182cd224e7fe90321374e.webm?t=1770887459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/0416877091b182cd224e7fe90321374e.mp4?t=1770887459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>众多可以进一步沉浸式享受音乐游戏的辅助设置</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在可以调整音符流速的基础上，还能修改连击数的显示位置、 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更改音符的设计等，来打造更加方便游玩的舒适环境。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/f0dfb81436e86c24306d18e1c9f83941.avif?t=1770887459\" width=600 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >登场角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内有超过80名东方角色登场，角色们都有Live2D的灵动动画。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/b9da4661aade322d64e6efc54583f5ee.avif?t=1770887459\" width=600 height=298 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/b6ddfbb0484e434c6229c8acd2e61f03.poster.avif?t=1770887459\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/b6ddfbb0484e434c6229c8acd2e61f03.webm?t=1770887459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/b6ddfbb0484e434c6229c8acd2e61f03.mp4?t=1770887459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为游戏增添色彩的精美插画</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推进游戏的过程中，能获得300多种御魂卡。皆由榎宮祐（NO GAME NO LIFE 游戏人生）、春场葱（五等分的新娘）等豪华画师阵容绘制。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/5dd5fc21bc18439b32ebfaf554e4d48d.avif?t=1770887459\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190220/extras/91cd9bf435f1e000c5eb3041edb3c0cd.avif?t=1770887459\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >唯一可以玩到东方Project原曲的音乐游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅仅只是实装了众多东方Project原曲，Toby Fox &amp; ZUN为本游戏专门制作的 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作曲《U.N. Owen Was Hero？》也以正在以免费DLC的形式发布 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏本篇中实装的原曲</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽霊楽団　～ Phantom Ensemble</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ハルトマンの妖怪少女</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ボーダーオブライフ</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >U.N.オーエンは彼女なのか？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紅楼　～ Eastern Dream…</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >月まで届け、不死の煙</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ピュアヒューリーズ　～ 心の在処</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过追加乐曲包（DLC）解锁的原曲 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第1弹: 恋色マスタースパーク </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第2弹: 千年幻想郷　～ History of the Moon </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第3弹: 輝かしき弱肉強食の掟 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第4弹: 亡き王女の為のセプテット</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第5弹: 神々が恋した幻想郷</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第6弹: 世界は可愛く出来ている </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第7弹: デザイアドライブ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第8弹: 少女綺想曲　～ Dream Battle </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第9弹: 偶像に世界を委ねて　〜 Idoratrize World </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第10弹: ほおずきみたいに紅い魂 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第11弹: 弾幕を持て、バレットフィリア達よ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第12弹: クレイジーバックダンサーズ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第13弹: 今宵は飄逸なエゴイスト(Live ver)　～ Egoistic Flowers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加乐曲包第14弹: 希望の星は青霄に昇る／龍王殺しのプリンセス</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >免费DLC </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >U.N. Owen Was Hero？<br>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >また紫桜の下に</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >決別の旅</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天衣無縫(not)innocent?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空しき骸のメガロヴァニア</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Necrolovania</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help me, ERINNNNNN!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >廻れ幻想フェスティバル</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揺籃の唄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『モノポリスティックタイクーン』</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >まちかどの『みこさま』</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯一無二のシミュラークル</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Re:Unknown X (marasy with 弦楽四重奏)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
